  "description": [
    "The prices on many food products have declined PIGGLY WIGGLY as usual givesits patrons the benefit of amarket de clines The prices quoted below will Interest every housewife In Wash ington as they tell her that she can now buy with 100 what would probably have cost her 150 three months ago PIGGLY WIGGLY Stores do not offer a few ials at cost or below cost and expect to make up the loss by ove ing other Items All items are sold at a small margin of profit at PIGGLY WIGGLY When you enter a PIGGLY WIGGLY Store you see around you old true and tried friends You see on the shelves nationally advertised goods whose reputation is unquestioned Nationally ad vertised goods are not known and used simply because they are nationally advertised but because they have stood the acid test they have been approved by the buying public as to quality and price Best Granulated Sugar perlb13c Gold Medal Flour24lbSack 169 Gold Medal Flour 121b Sa85C Gold Medal Flour 6lb Sack45C Flavo Nature Flavored Flour i160 Flavo Nature Flavored Flour 81C Flavo Nature Flavored Flour 41C Mt Vernon Corn Meal 12lb Sack41C o MtVernon Corn Meal 6lb Sack21C"
